$interpreted: Naya: Angel, WHAT WERE YOU THINKING?!
Naya: If the Tax Officer recognized you, we'd be finished!
Angelia: But I can't watch Nigel get into a fight with them.
Angelia: With proper communication, the issue would be resolved.
Naya: I can't take this anymore...
Angelia: What's that sound?
Naya: That sound, could it be the monster alert?!
Angelia: Aren't the soldiers around? Why have the monsters made it in?
Naya: It's not safe here! SCRAM!
Naya: Damn! There's so many of them!
Nigel: Careful, both of you!
Nigel: What happened, I thought you were scared of even a dog's fart?
Nigel: Best go hide indoors. No use bumbling around out here.
Naya: What's that supposed to mean?!
Angelia: You two, cut it out. Nigel, where's Lio?
Nigel: Hyacinthus took him into hiding. Lots of monsters are roaming the Slums,
Nigel: and I'm going to kill them all!
Angelia: We're gonna help!
Nigel: You!?
Angelia: This is our home, of course we're going to defend it. Naya, you too!
Naya: Yeah, yeah, got it.
Nigel: Whatever. But if you get into trouble, I've no time to rescue damsels in distress.
Angelia: Naya will protect me, we'll be safe. Let's split up. Naya, we'll take this side!
